<h1>Log In</h1>
<%= form_tag sessions_path do %>
  <div>
    <%= label_tag "email" %><br/>
    <%= text_field_tag "email" %>
  </div>
  <div>
    <%= label_tag :password %><br/>
    <%= password_field_tag :password %>
  </div>
  <div><%= submit_tag "Log In" %></div>
<% end %>
<!-- 
For the same reason we didn't instantiate an object in our users#new action, 
we haven't used a form_for here. It's a simple form_tag which will submit a POST 
request to the sessions_path, triggering our sessions#create action.  -->